    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything is just so quiet now. i wake up and for a split second i forget... and then the silence hits me again. it's like the house is just an empty shell. there's no point in even making coffee or doing anything. it feels like i'm just a ghost walking through rooms that don't belong to me anymore. i don't know how anyone is supposed to just keep existing like this.",
